{"tha-ap259:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap259:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap259:0.3":"Manjaripujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap259:1.1":"“Manjarikam karitvana, ","tha-ap259:1.2":"rathiyam patipajjaham; ","tha-ap259:1.3":"Addasam samananaggam, ","tha-ap259:1.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam. ","tha-ap259:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap259:2.2":"paramaya ca pitiya; ","tha-ap259:2.3":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap259:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap259:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap259:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap259:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap259:3.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap259:4.1":"Ito tesattatikappe, ","tha-ap259:4.2":"eko asim mahipati; ","tha-ap259:4.3":"Jotiyo nama namena, ","tha-ap259:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap259:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap259:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap259:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap259:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma manjaripujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap259:7.1":"Manjaripujakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}